{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>When I woke up, I noticed a strange hole in the ceiling of my room...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370760/extras/AHIMR_Ch1.jpg?t=1734387552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My name is James. I don\u2019t know why I\u2019m here, nor do I know what\u2019s behind this door! I\u2019m trapped in a colorless space with strange lines an environment that resembles my room, except with a hole in the ceiling. A strange object covers the hole to keep the light from coming in. The only thing I know is that I\u2019m not alone here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370760/extras/Gif01.gif?t=1734387552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<strong>A Hole in My Room</strong>&quot; is a Psychological Horror game. In this demo version, which includes the First Chapter of the game, you start the story and must find hidden objects, solve various puzzles, hide from dark creatures... But remember, you\u2019re not alone! So, hide whenever you sense danger. Find a way out as quickly as possible, before the strange, dark creature finds you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370760/extras/Gif02.gif?t=1734387552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo version has two difficulty levels right now, so if you need more guidance to solve the puzzles or get tired of the chase in the game, you can choose the easy mode. I also tried to add a few achievements for the demo version, so solve the puzzles and explore the dark environments! also I tried to design the game environments by drawing inspiration from the &quot;Meatly&quot; art style, so I hope you enjoy this artistic style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370760/extras/Gif03.gif?t=1734387552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re not alone, but who or what is looking \u00a0for you?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370760/extras/Gif04.gif?t=1734387552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Demo Features :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022  Duration: ~ 30min</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Discover story of the first chapter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Solve some different puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Find hidden objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Open locked doors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Hide from enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Enjoy the game art style </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/a43d522ec65488631d1ec67f04b1b4fbb827c097.jpg"},{"name":"Hide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/6a46c863c4a15a16cd90c5c5ee4d0e2eb9003e1d.jpg"},{"name":"Paper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/bb4b272d7fd8c9b053dd185333f1d61df35c80d5.jpg"},{"name":"SafeBox","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/e1c62f91b2e29c666b70d927a8f7082217ea3cc7.jpg"},{"name":"Upside down","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/43acc892107d59c4d42b3c23b51bb6d5e656730e.jpg"},{"name":"Lightup","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/60576fc7f34ef192525abb3860a807c775b12084.jpg"},{"name":"Secret Key","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3370760/723c77c18d776a6b4de0d048be0ed074a3bf8146.jpg"},{"name":"Dark Room","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam